ul.li:
Added support for DEFAULT nested layout parameters. You can now write:
                        
                            ${file-contents:${basedir}/file.txt}
                            ${rot13:URYYB}

Added [DefaultParameter] attribute which allows for nameless parameters	to layout renderers:
                        
                            ${aspnet-application}
                            ${aspnet-request}
                            ${aspnet-session}
                            ${date}
                            ${environment}
                            ${file-contents}
                            ${gdc}
                            ${mdc}
                            ${process-info}
                            ${special-folder}
                            ${asp-application}
                            ${asp-request}
                            ${asp-session}
